// 96-Channel NSP mapping
//							
// Data is as follows 'c r b e l'							
//   c - 0 based column from left to right							
//   r - 0 based row from bottom to top							
//   b - bank name - values can be A, B, C, or D							
//   e - 1 based electrode number within the bank - values can be 1-32							
//   l - label used to rename channels in Central							
//							
// Comments begin with //							
// First non-comment line is the Mapfile description							
//							
